    "asOf": "2023-07-11",
    "date": "2024-06-25T14:01:10Z",
    "text": "Federal Election Audit Act\n\nThis bill allows states to use requirements payments from the Election Assistance Commission to conduct postelection audits. In particular, a state may use such a payment to conduct and publish an audit of (1) the effectiveness and accuracy of the voting systems, election procedures, and outcomes used to carry out a federal election in the state; and (2) the performance of the state and local election officials who carried out the election. \u00a0"
  },
